Date: Mon, 14 Aug 2023 18:13:57 -0500
Subject: [PATCH] ASoC: Intel: soc-acpi: add support for Dell SKU0C87 devices
Git-commit: fec75606f48f6c85eca8a9e868e41fb657abd1ca
Patch-mainline: v6.6-rc1
References: jsc#PED-6045 jsc#PED-6036 jsc#PED-6104 jsc#PED-6114 jsc#PED-6067 jsc#PED-6123

This patch adds the acpi match table for Dell SKU0C87
devices, the codec layout is:
    SDW0: RT714 DMIC
    SDW1: RT1318 Speaker
    SDW2: RT1318 Speaker

Note that there is no jack codec on SKU0C87 devices.

